description:
Season: 19
Original Air Date: 4/14/2006

Bail is again denied for Jackie. Eric urges Jackie to remain strong.  A mysterious figure enters the Jackie M Boutique.  Later when Nick stops by to check on things he is shocked to find Megan in Jackie’s office. Christian and Dante discuss the situation of Dino now that Felicia is alive. Dante is protective and tells Christian to stay out of it.  Felicia eases Bridget’s nerves and tells Bridget that Dino will always be a part of her life.  They agree to raise Dino together.
